LE SCAMPI CONDOMINIUM ASSOCIATION, INC., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
CN INDIAN SHORES, LLC, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-5108 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 25, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

This appeal is dismissed because of the appellant's failure to satisfy this court's December 28, 2017, fee order.

NORTHCUTT, BLACK, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
